prompt.title: Embedding for The Evolution of Programming Languages
prompt.content: The evolution of programming languages has progressed from physical rewiring of vacuum tubes through low-level machine code to high-level languages like Python and JavaScript. The next revolution in this evolution is the use of natural language for writing software.
